    "Id": "956944",
    "ThreadId": "406993",
    "Html": "\r\n<p>Modify the ControlTemplate of the EdgeControl. You can find the default ControlTemplate here:</p>\r\n<p>http://graphsharp.codeplex.com/SourceControl/changeset/view/9c108fe2dfa4#Source/Graph#.Controls/Themes/Generic.xaml</p>\r\n",
    "PostedDate": "2012-12-17T05:51:20.32-08:00",
